@startuml sequence_slave

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName Monospaced
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2

title modbus_c -- Slave Request/Reply Sequence (Serial <-> PDU Handler)

participant "Serial / TTY" as SERIAL
participant "rtu.c\nSlave State Machine" as RTU
participant "rtu_memory.c\nPDU Handler" as PDU_CB

== Slave receives frame ==

SERIAL -> RTU : serial_recv_cb(byte)\n[repeated for each byte]
RTU -> RTU : IDLE -> SOF\nstart 1.5t timer
RTU -> RTU : SOF -> RECV\n(bytes 2..N)
RTU -> RTU : 1.5t timeout\nRECV -> EOF
RTU -> RTU : 3.5t timeout\nEOF -> IDLE
RTU -> RTU : adu_check()\nCRC verify
RTU -> PDU_CB : pdu_cb(state, addr, fcode,\n  begin, end, curr,\n  dst_begin, dst_end, user_data)
PDU_CB -> PDU_CB : validate address\nread memory region
PDU_CB --> RTU : dst_curr (reply end pointer)
RTU -> RTU : append reply CRC\nRTU_STATE_BUSY
RTU -> SERIAL : serial_send(state)

== Error path: slave replies with exception ==

note over RTU, PDU_CB
  If fcode unsupported or address out of range,
  pdu_cb returns exception frame:
  [addr | fcode+0x80 | ecode | CRC]
end note

@enduml
